      <body><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><date when="1898-02-04">4/II 1898</date></dateline></opener><p><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00001-000-00244"/>Lieber Arthur, </salute>
               also heute Abends im <rs ref="#pmb42812" type="place">Caffee Royal</rs> (<anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KLM20191115-1"/><rs ref="#pmb42812" type="place">Scheuchen<pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00001-000-00245"/>stuhl</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KLM20191115-1h">Richtig: <rs ref="#pmb42812" type="place">Café
                     Scheuchenstuel</rs>. Ein Wechsel zu Name <rs ref="#pmb42812" type="place">Café
                     Royal</rs> lässt sich nicht verifizieren.</note>) Ecke der <rs ref="#pmb729" type="place">Schuler</rs> u. <rs ref="#pmb42815" type="place">Stroblgasse</rs>.</p><closer><hi rend="underline" n="1">Von Herzen Ihr</hi><lb/><signed>Richard</signed></closer></div></body>
